Annotation ----> Hashie nevisi (Mani)
    ----> Alamateshan ----> Haman @ poshteshon ast.
    ---> dar HTML ha estefade mishavand
    ----> Be tanhaie kari ra anjam nemidahad.


Ahdafe estefade az annotationha:
Yekseri khata va ieradha ra be compiler bedim.
Mogheye compile source code ra avaz konim
Mogheye Run-Time source code ra avaz konim

******************************************************

Mazaya:
1. Rajebe khataha va varning ha be compiler etela midahad.
2. Mogheye compile sorce code ra avaz mikonad.
***********************************************************

Dar zamane runtime --> ye raftary ra avaz konad.
**********************************************************'

Jaye gharargereftan :
Bala sare class ha - Balasare method ha - Balasare field ha - balasare interface ha - Balasare  package ha -
Hameja mitavanim estefade konim
**********************************************

Daste-bandi ha:
1. Java Built-in Annotation:
    ---> Jozve hadafhaye aval hastand ---> khataha va hoshdar ha ra be compiler etela midahand
  @Override     @FunctionalInterface    @SuppressWarning
  @Deprecated   @SafeVarargs            @Native

2. Meta Annotation:
    ---> Zamani estefade mishavand ke khodemon bekhahim ye Annotation benevisim.
    @Target
    @Retention  ---> SOURCE --> Baraye hoshdar --> Na mogheye Run-time be dard mikhore na moghe compile
                ---> CLASS --> Baraye compiler ghabele moshahedast
                ---> RUNTIME --> Ham baraye runtime ham baraye compile ghabele moshahedast
         !!! --> agar nagozarim be sorate pishfarz --> CLASS ra migozarad.
    @Inherited  ----> Baraye ers bordeshodane annotation ha.
        !!! --> Dar ersbary ha Annotation ers borde nemishavad.
    @Dcumented  ---> usage an Annotation ra dar Java DOC neshondahad.
    @Repeatable  ---> Ye jahaie majborimchandbar az ye Annotation bishtar az yekbar roye yek element estefade konim.

*******************************************************'
@SuppressWarning ---> khataheye compiler ra migirad --> ghesmathaie ke be range ghahveie darmiayand.
@Deprecated ---> Khode JDK ro methode khat mikeshe ---> JDK dar versione jadid nemikhahad on Method ra erae bede.
            ---> Karbordesh dar API ha ast --> baraye inke be sherkat haye dge befahmanim ke in service digar ghararnist edame peida konad
@Native ---> To khode JDK estefade mishavad.
        ---> Dare az code Native stefade mikonad --> Dataye avalye dar java.
@SafeVarargs ---> baraye zamani ke ye method ba vorodie list ya array dashte bashim test(String ... s){ }

**********************************************************'

SAKHTE ANNOTATION

public @interface MyAnnotation{  }

Bayad chand chiz ra baraye an tarif konim:
1. Gharare Balasare che chizi estefade shavad.
